cryptpad-description =
    CryptPad is a privacy-first, end-to-end encrypted collaborative office suite.

    All documents are encrypted in your browser before being sent to the server —
    the server stores only ciphertext and can never read your data. CryptPad supports
    rich text documents, code editors, spreadsheets, presentations, whiteboards,
    kanban boards, and forms. Teams collaborate in real time without sacrificing privacy.

cryptpad-features =
    - End-to-end encryption — server never sees plaintext
    - Rich text, code, spreadsheets, presentations, whiteboards
    - Kanban boards and forms
    - Real-time collaborative editing
    - No account required for guests (via share link)
    - OIDC integration for registered users
    - Zero-knowledge architecture
